42
00:04:33,869 --> 00:04:41,318
Like, that's the level of attention that law enforcement were placing on these two young people driving down the street doing nothing wrong in their car.

43
00:04:42,612 --> 00:04:46,373
Inevitably, as you likely can imagine, they are stopped by a number of cars.

44
00:04:46,753 --> 00:05:05,036
