49
00:05:22,667 --> 00:05:27,271
You know, you'd almost thought they had just been observed robbing a bank, which they did not, just to be clear.

50
00:05:27,792 --> 00:05:30,654
You know, and so, unfortunately, these are two young people.

51
00:05:31,515 --> 00:05:56,363
the Black young man is sort of brought out of the car first, again with this behavior of like, you know, walk backwards and walk slowly and keep your hands in sight and things of that nature, while his partner, the young lady in the car, Habak, is told, as she kind of looks back fearfully for her friend, she's told, face forward, keep your eyes straight, don't turn your head, and all of the time remember that there are guns, there are guns,

52
00:05:56,743 --> 00:05:58,945
pointed at my clients, these two young people.

53
00:05:59,625 --> 00:06:08,452
