55
00:06:13,628 --> 00:06:29,214
After all of this, after a number of attempts to get information when they're not given any information, after the car is searched sort of under duress by Jeremiah, who's like, I mean, I'm standing here in cuffs with guns pointed at me and you want to search my car, I suppose, what else do you say?

56
00:06:29,274 --> 00:06:30,674
But yes, you may search my car.

57
00:06:32,135 --> 00:06:32,955
The car is searched.

