98
00:12:08,835 --> 00:12:21,404
Here we don't even have that strenuous of an investigation occurring because this is not something at this point that has raised the specter of sort of criminal liability, which is why the DA's office would normally look into it.

99
00:12:22,085 --> 00:12:28,910
