139
00:16:10,377 --> 00:16:12,818
So I think we are going in the right direction.

140
00:16:13,298 --> 00:16:16,879
You know, the reality is that nothing good in life happens quickly.

141
00:16:16,899 --> 00:16:17,620
That's just true.

142
00:16:18,844 --> 00:16:27,827
