148
00:17:13,432 --> 00:17:16,614
But I think as a collective, people are starting to get it.

149
00:17:16,894 --> 00:17:19,196
People are starting to figure out the vocab and the jargon.

150
00:17:19,216 --> 00:17:21,277
They are starting to see where the pressure points are.

151
00:17:21,297 --> 00:17:26,100
