153
00:17:28,282 --> 00:17:31,304
We're going to continue to blast them out in the media, just like you guys are.

154
00:17:31,644 --> 00:17:37,808
We are not going to sit idly by while people continue to decide that this is going to be policing as usual, because policing as usual is over.

155
00:17:38,369 --> 00:17:38,729
It's over.

156
00:17:39,269 --> 00:17:44,959
