164
00:18:03,715 --> 00:18:07,600
So one thing I'll tell you is I didn't really know much about Medford before this case, to be quite honest.

165
00:18:08,621 --> 00:18:11,344
I had not had any clients from the area before.

166
00:18:11,384 --> 00:18:13,587
I've not worked on any cases against the city or town.

167
00:18:14,558 --> 00:18:34,364
